同意授權













論文中文名稱：智慧財產權管理策略研究 -以新創公司為例
														[以論文名稱查詢館藏系統]
													


論文英文名稱：Study on Strategy of Intellectual Property Rights Management-Startup Company
														[以論文名稱查詢館藏系統]
													


院校名稱：臺北科技大學


學院名稱：人文與社會科學學院


系所名稱：智慧財產權研究所


畢業學年度：104


畢業學期：第二學期


出版年度：105


中文姓名：周明毅


英文姓名：Ming-Yi Chou


研究生學號：101A48013


學位類別：碩士


語文別：中文


口試日期：2016/07/26


指導教授中文名：江雅綺


指導教授英文名：Ya-Chi Chang


口試委員中文名：蔡鴻文；陳省三；江雅綺


口試委員英文名：Ya-Chi Chang


中文關鍵詞：智慧財產權、專利、商標、商業策略、智財管理


英文關鍵詞：Intellectual property rights, Patents, Business strategy, Intellectual property management


論文中文摘要：所謂的智慧財產權，就法律面而言指專利法、商標法、著作權法及營業秘密法等，法條中都有明確規定其權利義務，而要取得專利權及商標權都是要向各國國家的專利商標權責機關申請，在台灣專利權責機關為經濟部智慧財產局，而申請費及每年維護費用累積會是筆可觀的數字，許多智慧財產權管理研究都針對國內外上市上櫃公司所進行的研究，國外知名的如IBM、APPLE及GOOGLE，國內如ASUS、台積電及鴻海等，都是屬於技術層次高及資金雄厚公司，因此在智慧財產權管理策略上，比較沒有資金成本負擔，然對於新創公司(資本額5000萬以下)而言，並無法投入大量資金進行智財策略管理及佈局，而在全球競爭環境下，科技的進步與轉變，總是需要新創公司產生，才能保有其經濟優勢，避免國家失去競爭力而被邊緣化，因此市場是需要新創公司，而新創公司在資金不足及技術困境下，如何完善的制定智慧財產權管理策略，有其研究的必要性，期許本研究成果可成為新創公司在制定智慧財產管理策略的一個參考資料。


論文英文摘要：The so-called intellectual property rights. The law terms means the patent law, trademark law, copyright law and trade secret law, etc. The law has clearly defined rights and obligations. In order to obtain a patent and trademark rights that need to apply by national authority of patent and trademark. Patent authority is the Ministry of Economic Affairs Intellectual Property Office in Taiwan. The application fee and annual maintenance fee will be accumulated considerable expense. Many Intellectual Property Rights Management studies that focus on publicly traded companies conducted include domestic and foreign. Well-known abroad, such as IBM, APPLE and GOOGLE, domestic such as ASUS, TSMC and Hon Hai, etc. They are of high technical level and well-funded company. Therefore, in intellectual property management strategy, there is no comparative capital cost burden. However, for startup (capital of 50 million or less) is concerned, and can not invest a lot of money for intellectual property policy management and layout. The global competitive environment. Technology progress and change. Always need to generate start-up Companies. In order to maintain their economic advantages. To avoid loss of national competitiveness and marginalized. So the market is the need to create new company. startup company in case of insufficient funds and technical difficulties. How to complete development of intellectual property management strategy is necessary to study.


